
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ Rule configurations are explained below.","color":"gold"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"white"},{"text":"    Toggle Automatic Judge    When set to ON, the system will automatically apply game rules at the end of each turn in both singleplayer and multiplayer, such as awarding ball-in-hand, resetting balls, or changing scores. When OFF, players must manually execute rules via suggested chat/commands, cheat needs to be allowed.","color":"gray"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"white"},{"text":"    Toggle Foul Feedbacks    When set to ON, the system will display the reason for a foul when it occurs. Requires Automatic Judge to be enabled.","color":"white"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"white"},{"text":"    Toggle Rail Requirement    When set to ON, rail-related rules will be enforced in 8-ball and 9-ball. For example, in 9-ball, after the cue ball first contacts the target ball, at least one ball must hit a rail or be pocketed. Requires Automatic Judge to be enabled.","color":"gray"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"white"},{"text":"    Toggle SP Role Switch    When set to ON, in singleplayer 8-ball, the system will automatically switch the player's role after a turn ends (e.g., switching between solids and stripes). Requires Automatic Judge to be enabled.","color":"white"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ End of Help...","color":"gray"}]

tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇ 以下是自定义规则的说明","color":"gold"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇　　","color":"white"},{"text":"使用自动裁判　　开启此功能时自动裁判会在单人/多人游戏回合结束时给出基于游戏规则的判定，例如给予玩家自由球，复位，罚分等。关闭此功能时玩家需要通过聊天栏提示手动执行各种规则，需要允许作弊。","color":"gray"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇　　","color":"white"},{"text":"输出犯规信息　　开启此功能时自动裁判会在犯规时给出犯规的原因。需要开启自动裁判。","color":"white"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇　　","color":"white"},{"text":"执行碰库要求　　开启此功能时自动裁判会在八球和九球游戏中执行和碰库相关的要求，例如在九球游戏中母球第一次接触目标球后必须有任意球碰库或落袋。需要开启自动裁判。","color":"gray"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇　　","color":"white"},{"text":"单人角色切换　　开启此功能时自动裁判会使八球游戏的单人玩家切换角色，例如打全色球时连杆结束后，切换至打花色球的角色。需要开启自动裁判。","color":"white"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇ 帮助结束...","color":"gray"}]
